Start to 2011 was excellent. Had meditation, Internet date, bikram yoga session, dinner w mum, went to beach, rescued friend, did juicing
bring on birth brilliant yr 2011. it's a yr of energizing change, opportunities, challenges and growth. step out comfort zone, let go & fly
Goodbye 2010. hello 2011 year of Rabbit. it's either fr prosperity or plague. Yr choice. set yr intentions tonite & Energise them fr a wk
Gratitude takes us out of Ego & into presence. It transcends our fears & doubts. Look at 2010 w gratitude  and expect bigger better 2011
Melbournians rejoice. it's a cracker day. current 26 to top 29 degrees, cool breeze, bright sunshine, 26% humidity, enjoy while it lasts
did Bikram yoga last nite. 90 mins of good mind body bending torture. not felt so stuffed fr long time & no sex. instructress was hot
Friend had serious accident. Broke collar bone & was unconscious. Accidents are Incidents requiring Action by Universe. Its wake up call.
just had awesome tuina remedial Chinese massage w Mark Mayes, expert in Chinese medicine, qi gong & tai chi. feel great, loose & relaxed
Seasons salutations. Christmas was fab food, family, fun, frenzy (not fr me), fellowship, frivolous presents & funny. Set time to Relax now
had lovely swim at south beach Fremantle. warm 32 degrees. ocean swim is great fr body, refreshing grounding energizing. all stress released
Riding motorbike from Manjimup to Perth. Its slightly damp. Had great wend with organic farmer friend Wayne Edwards on his 50th birthday.
it's warm in Perth 30 degrees. had great time sunbaking on grass, dip in pool & more of same. sunshine great fr health, Vit D & vitality
The Ancients said "Accept and u  become whole. Once whole, the world is as your home. what u resist Persists
met w 12  men in rare mens group in Darlington Perth where we shared fr our hearts things not usually expressed. powerful poignant healing
it's 36 degrees in Perth. beautiful. went fr motorbike ride @ mundering weir hills. having coffee at camel farm. magical experiences.
You only SEE when u still the mind, suspend judgement, stories & emotions. This is not easy, requires discipline & time
Today is energy of Beauty. It's in eye of beholder. Take time to look, see things as they are; not what u think. Look appreciate w gratitude
just finished most awesome 7 day silent retreat. spent time connecting deeply w self & healing v  deep buried hurts. senses & mind v clear
Had coffee in Leederville w surgeon Reg Lee & engineer Paul Gillbanks (XL). Most wonderful conversation & men. Check out Reg on Facebook.
melbourne today turned up 4 seasons in a day. It was extreme. Pouring rain morn, warm sunshine midday, huge storm mid anoon closed airport
Today is a beautiful Day.... I hope you have smiled at someone today and appreciate all that you have...
